ATM_Startup(){

    if (Card == true)
        return a message asking for pin

    read pin from user
    send information to the bank database
}
Verify_Pin(){

    read card information
    read the pin 
    cross reference with the bank database
    request profile from bank if data can be confirmed
    return error message if pin is incorrect
}
Error(){
    card information and pin do not match, 
    A message is returned to the customer 
    and the failed attempt is noted. 
}

Profile_Request(){

    Sends request to bank to send all account information
    returns true

}
Profile_Verified(){
    account is verified and information is sent to the user
}
Menu(){
    Menu will return the balances of each account
    Menu will give user options on actions they are allowed to do 
    View current amounts, deposits money, withdrawal money
        Deposits and withdrawals amounts are sent to Update()
    End the session   
}
Update(){
    Takes the amount withdrawn and deposited and updates the balance. 
    Will make the user verify pin again
    else the session will end
}